OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChance of a light shower across
OL,6,Fthe west and north this morning.
OL,7,FOtherwise it will be dry with some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells, some cloud
OL,9,Fbubbling up by afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fclear periods. Staying dry overnight
OL,13,Fbut clouding over across the southwest
OL,14,Flater. Strengthening southwesterly
OL,15,Fwinds along the west coast. Cold with
OL,16,Fsome frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
