OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FSome brightness along the
OL,6,FMoray coast otherwise rather cloudy.
OL,7,FOutbreaks of rain will spread
OL,8,Fnortheast through the day, mainly
OL,9,Faffecting the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FCloudy with rain spreading east on
OL,13,FThursday, becoming drier from the west
OL,14,Flater. Dry and bright on Friday and
OL,15,FSaturday. Strong southwesterly winds
OL,16,Facross the far northwest on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
